<p>After finishing the firmware, I saw that I could have chosen something even smaller but I wanted to err on the safe side. Shipping isnâ€™t free! (i actually had a coupon and it was).</p>

<p>This project is meant to be complimentary with an USB IR Receiver which is still a Work in Progress, aimed at controlling my computer from a distance while watching movies; for example to pause it or change the volume.</p>

