<h2 id="the-pic10f322">The PIC10F322</h2>

<p>This microcontroller contains:</p>
<ul>
  <li>0.896 KB Flash</li>
  <li>64 B SRAM</li>
  <li>16 MHz Internal Oscillator</li>
</ul>
